<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p class="updated">Last updated: March 3, 2026</p>

<p>Balaji Balineni ("we," "us," or "our") operates the Tik Video Saver & Downloader mobile application (the "App"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our App.</p>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
<p>We are committed to minimizing data collection. The App is designed to function without requiring you to create an account or provide personal information.</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Video URLs:</strong> When you paste or share a video link, the URL is sent to our servers solely to fetch the video for download. We do not store these URLs after the download completes.</li>
    <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> We may collect anonymized, non-personally-identifiable device information (device model, OS version, app version) for crash reporting and performance improvement.</li>
    <li><strong>Purchase Data:</strong> If you subscribe to a premium plan, payment is processed entirely by Apple through the App Store. We do not collect, store, or have access to your payment details.</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. Information We Do Not Collect</h2>
<ul>
    <li>We do not collect your name, email address, or phone number.</li>
    <li>We do not access your contacts, camera, or microphone.</li>
    <li>We do not track your location.</li>
    <li>We do not collect or store your TikTok account credentials.</li>
    <li>We do not sell, rent, or share any user data with third parties.</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Photo Library Access</h2>
<p>The App requests access to your Photo Library solely to save downloaded videos. This access is used only when you initiate a save action. We do not read, scan, or upload any existing photos or videos from your library.</p>

<h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>The App may use the following third-party services:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Apple App Store:</strong> For in-app purchases and subscription management.</li>
    <li><strong>Video Processing API:</strong> To fetch and process video downloads. Only the video URL you provide is sent to this service.</li>
</ul>

<h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
<p>Video URLs are processed in real time and are not stored on our servers after the download is complete. Downloaded videos are stored locally on your device and are under your full control.</p>

<h2>6. Children's Privacy</h2>
<p>The App is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe a child has provided us with personal data, please contact us so we can delete it.</p>

<h2>7. Data Security</h2>
<p>We use industry-standard security measures, including HTTPS encryption for all network communications, to protect your data during transmission. Since we do not store personal data on our servers, the risk of a data breach affecting your personal information is minimal.</p>

<h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
<p>Since we do not collect personal data, there is generally no personal data for us to provide, modify, or delete. If you have any concerns about your data, please contact us.</p>

<h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated revision date. Continued use of the App after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.</p>

